strings: <voice_0x0100173D><se_high>Princess Medea: My marriage was arranged by our two families long ago. I thought I had no choice but to accept it gracefully.

<voice_0x0100173E><se_high>Princess Medea: I always resigned myself to it.
I always saw it as my duty as princess. But...
<voice_0x0100173F><se_high>Princess Medea: I simply can't abide him! If it's a choice between marrying that twit and being a horse, you can make mine a grass sandwich!

<voice_0x01001740><se_high>Princess Medea: I can't live my whole life denying my
true feelings!
<voice_0x01001741><se_high>Princess Medea: Take my hand and let's run away together! Please, <hero>, take me away from here!
